=\"Alt text\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1befad27f4b293c6b8b8eb3a984a9809/9144d/image.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1befad27f4b293c6b8b8eb3a984a9809/c26ae/image.png 158w,\n/static/1befad27f4b293c6b8b8eb3a984a9809/6bdcf/image.png 315w,\n/static/1befad27f4b293c6b8b8eb3a984a9809/9144d/image.png 401w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 401px) 100vw, 401px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>편집기에서는 오류를 내지 않는데, <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby develop</code>으로 개발 서버를 열려고 하니 에러를 내뿜는다.</p>\n\n          <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button-container\">\n            <div class=\"gatsby-remark-prismjs-copy-button\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" onclick=\"gatsbyRemarkCopyToClipboard(this, this.parentNode.nextElementSibling)\">\n              Copy\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"> ERROR <span class=\"token comment\">#98123  WEBPACK.DEVELOP</span>\n\nGenerating development JavaScript bundle failed\n\nModule build failed <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>from ./node_modules/css-loader/dist/cjs.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>:\nCssSyntaxError\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">91</span>:6<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> /home/ubuntu/workspace/10cheon00.github.io/src/styles/post.scss Unknown word\n\n  <span class=\"token number\">89</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> ul li,\n  <span class=\"token number\">90</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> ol li <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">91</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>   // padding-left: var<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--spacing-0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n     <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>      ^\n  <span class=\"token number\">92</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>   margin-bottom: <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token number\">93</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>   margin-top: var<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--spacing-1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\nFile: src/style.scss:91:6\n\nfailed Re-building development bundle - <span class=\"token number\">0</span>.136s\nERROR <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> ./src/style.scss\nModule build failed <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>from ./node_modules/mini-css-extract-plugin/dist/loader.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>:\nModuleBuildError: Module build failed <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>from ./node_modules/css-loader/dist/cjs.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>:\nCssSyntaxError\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">91</span>:6<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> /home/ubuntu/workspace/10cheon00.github.io/src/styles/post.scss Unknown word\n\n  <span class=\"token number\">89</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> ul li,\n  <span class=\"token number\">90</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> ol li <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">91</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>   // padding-left: var<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--spacing-0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n     <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>      ^\n  <span class=\"token number\">92</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>   margin-bottom: <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token number\">93</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>   margin-top: var<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--spacing-1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    at processResult <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>/home/ubuntu/workspace/10cheon00.github.io/node_modules/webpack/lib/NormalModule.js:764:19<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    at /home/ubuntu/workspace/10cheon00.github.io/node_modules/webpack/lib/NormalModule.js:866:5\n    at /home/ubuntu/workspace/10cheon00.github.io/node_modules/loader-runner/lib/LoaderRunner.js:400:11\n    at /home/ubuntu/workspace/10cheon00.github.io/node_modules/loader-runner/lib/LoaderRunner.js:252:18\n    at context.callback <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>/home/ubuntu/workspace/10cheon00.github.io/node_modules/loader-runner/lib/LoaderRunner.js:124:13<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    at Object.loader <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>/home/ubuntu/workspace/10cheon00.github.io/node_modules/css-loader/dist/index.js:155:5<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n @ ./gatsby-browser.js <span class=\"token number\">16</span>:0-26\n @ ./.cache/api-runner-browser-plugins.js <span class=\"token number\">46</span>:10-41\n @ ./.cache/api-runner-browser.js <span class=\"token number\">3</span>:16-55\n @ ./.cache/app.js <span class=\"token number\">10</span>:0-65 <span class=\"token number\">28</span>:87-32:1 <span class=\"token number\">36</span>:20-29 <span class=\"token number\">64</span>:0-14 <span class=\"token number\">87</span>:19-28 <span class=\"token number\">122</span>:6-15 <span class=\"token number\">28</span>:0-32:2\n\n<span class=\"token number\">1</span> ERROR <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> child compilations <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Use <span class=\"token string\">'stats.children: true'</span> resp. <span class=\"token string\">'--stats-children'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token function\">more</span> details<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://sass-lang.com/documentation/syntax/comments/\">공식 문서</a>에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">//</code>을 사용하지 않고 대신 <code class=\"language-text\">/* */</code>을 사용하도록 되어 있다.</p>\n<p>그러니까 vscode내에서 주석 형식이 <code class=\"language-text\">//</code>로 처리되는 것이 문제다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"해결법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"해결법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>해결법</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/68745974\">linux - Is it possible to use \"/\" in a filename? - Stack Overflow</a></p>\n<p>해결법은 간단하다. 위 링크를 참조하면, vscode가 설치된 폴더에서 scss폴더 속 <code class=\"language-text\">language-configuration.json</code>파일을 열고 <code class=\"language-text\">lineComment</code> 속성의 값을 <code class=\"language-text\">\"\"</code>로 바꾸면 된다는 것이다.</p>\n<p>파일을 열기 위해 <code class=\"language-text\">WIN+R</code>을 눌러 실행창을 열고 <code class=\"language-text\">%LOCALAPPDATA%\\programs\\Microsoft VS Code\\resources\\app\\extensions\\scss</code>을 입력한다.</p>\n<p>그러면 scss폴더의 몇몇 설정들이 담긴 폴더가 열리는데 <code class=\"language-text\">language-configuration.json</code>파일을 연다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/691388bf667820bf55b076298dd075bf/4ff83/image-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 4.430379746835443%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAYAAADeko4lAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAUklEQVR42h3KOwqAMBBAQa8iJJuN+WIstLHRQvAGYiN4/ys8wamnEyeEaUFDRoeEr43YZjRVRBze9IhPDPtNOV/i8RC3izKt/9E8Ii7ircGK8gHVPR9P98JOKwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Alt text\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/691388bf667820bf55b076298dd075bf/f058b/image-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/691388bf667820bf55b076298dd075bf/c26ae/image-1.png 158w,\n/static/691388bf667820bf55b076298dd075bf/6bdcf/image-1.png 315w,\n/static/691388bf667820bf55b076298dd075bf/f058b/image-1.png 630w,\n/static/691388bf667820bf55b076298dd075bf/4ff83/image-1.png 843w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>한 줄밖에 없는 파일이 열리는데 바로 보이는 <code class=\"language-text\">lineComment</code>의 값을 <code class=\"language-text\">\"\"</code>로 바꾸면 해결된다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"vscode에서 scss의 주석 단축키가 이상한 이유","date":"November 09, 2023","description":null,"tags":["vscode","scss"]},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C\">문제</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0%EB%B2%95\">해결법</a></li>\n</ul>"},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/java/annotation/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Annotation","